msgctxt "an4.169:3.9"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo kāyassa bhedā sasaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a person becomes fully extinguished when the body breaks up by "
"making extra effort."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.169:4.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo diṭṭheva dhamme asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a person become fully extinguished in the present life without "
"making extra effort?"

msgctxt "an4.169:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … "
"dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ … pe … catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant … enters and remains in the first absorption … second "
"absorption … third absorption … fourth absorption …"

msgctxt "an4.169:4.3"
msgid "So imāni pañca sekhabalāni upanissāya viharati—"
msgstr "They rely on these five powers of a trainee:"

msgctxt "an4.169:4.4"
msgid "saddhābalaṃ … pe … paññābalaṃ."
msgstr "faith, conscience, prudence, energy, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an4.169:4.5"
msgid "Tassimāni pañcindriyāni adhimattāni pātubhavanti—"
msgstr "And they have these five faculties strongly:"

msgctxt "an4.169:4.6"
msgid "saddhindriyaṃ … pe … paññindriyaṃ."
msgstr "faith, energy, mindfulness, immersion, and wisdom."

msgctxt "an4.169:4.7"
msgid ""
