msgctxt "an4.169:4.8"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo diṭṭheva dhamme asaṅkhāraparinibbāyī hoti."
msgstr ""
"That’s how a person becomes fully extinguished in the present life without "
"making extra effort."

#. </p><p>
